Th\'f4ng tin v\f1\lang1066\u7873? vi\u7879?c s\u7917? d\u7909?ng \f4\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c thu th\u7853?p bao g\u7891?m d\u7919? li\u7879?u v\u7873? vi\u7879?c s\u7917? d\u7909?ng thi\u7871?t b\u7883? qua nh\u7853?t k\f0\lang1033\'fd l\f1\lang1066\u7883?ch s\u7917? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ho\f1\lang1066\u7841?t \f4\'f0\f1\u7897?ng c\u7911?a h\u7879? \f4\'f0i\f1\u7873?u h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh, tr\'ecnh duy\f1\lang1066\u7879?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\'e1c \f1\lang1066\u7913?ng d\u7909?ng ph\u7847?n m\u7873?m kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c. Vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c n\f0\lang1033\'e0y bao g\f1\lang1066\u7891?m nh\f4\u432?ng kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng gi\f1\lang1066\u7899?i h\u7841?n \u7903? nh\u7919?ng \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng \f4\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c c\f0\lang1033\'e0i \f4\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7863?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7917? d\u7909?ng tr\f0\lang1033\'ean thi\f1\lang1066\u7871?t b\u7883?, c\f4\u361?ng nh\u432? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c trang web \f4\'f0\f0\'e3 truy c\f1\lang1066\u7853?p t\u7915? thi\u7871?t b\u7883?. Th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin thu th\f1\lang1066\u7853?p \f4\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c tr\f0\lang1033\'ean thi\f1\lang1066\u7871?t b\u7883? c\u7911?a b\u7841?n s\u7869? kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng \f4\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c chia s\u7867? ho\u7863?c ti\u7871?t l\u7897? v\u7899?i b\u7845?t k\u7923? \f4\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f0\lang1033\'e1c n\'e0o ho\f1\lang1066\u7863?c c\f0\lang1033\'e1c b\'ean th\f1\lang1066\u7913? ba kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c tr\f1\lang1066\u7915? khi b\u7855?t bu\u7897?c theo lu\u7853?t hi\u7879?n h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh ho\f1\lang1066\u7863?c c\f0\lang1033\'f3 s\f1\lang1066\u7921? \f4\'f0\f1\u7891?ng \f0\lang1033\'fd r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a b\u7841?n.\par
