\bullet\tab N\f1\lang1066\u7871?\f0\lang1033 u c\'e1c thi\f1\lang1066\u7871?\f0\lang1033 t b\f1\lang1066\u7883?\f0\lang1033  v\'e0 h\f1\lang1066\u7879?\f2\lang1033  \'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?\f0\lang1033 u h\'e0nh c\f1\lang1066\u7911?\f0\lang1033 a b\f1\lang1066\u7841?\f2\lang1033 n \'f0\'e1\f0 p \f1\lang1066\u7913?\f0\lang1033 ng c\'e1c y\'eau c\f1\lang1066\u7847?\f0\lang1033 u c\f1\lang1066\u7911?\f0\lang1033 a ch\'fang t\'f4i (c\'f3 t\f1\lang1066\u7841?\f0\lang1033 i: {\cf0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK https://www.mcafee.com/vi-vn/consumer-support/help/system-requirement.html }}{\fldrslt{https://www.mcafee.com/vi-vn/consumer-support/help/system-requirement.html\ul0\cf0}}}}\f0\fs20 ). B\f1\lang1066\u7841?\f0\lang1033 n c\'f3 tr\'e1ch nhi\f1\lang1066\u7879?\f2\lang1033 m \'f0\f1\lang1066\u7843?\f0\lang1033 m b\f1\lang1066\u7843?\f0\lang1033 o thi\f1\lang1066\u7871?\f0\lang1033 t b\f1\lang1066\u7883?\f0\lang1033  c\f1\lang1066\u7911?\f0\lang1033 a m\'ecnh lu\'f4n c\f1\lang1066\u7853?\f0\lang1033 p nh\f1\lang1066\u7853?t v\'e0 \'f0\'e1p \u7913?\f0\lang1033 ng c\'e1c y\'eau c\f1\lang1066\u7847?\f2\lang1033 u \'f0\'f3. (Vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?\f2\lang1033 c \'f0\f1\lang1066\u7843?\f0\lang1033 m b\f1\lang1066\u7843?\f0\lang1033 o thi\f1\lang1066\u7871?\f0\lang1033 t b\f1\lang1066\u7883?\f0\lang1033  lu\'f4n c\f1\lang1066\u7853?\f0\lang1033 p nh\f1\lang1066\u7853?\f0\lang1033 t c\f4\u361?\f0 ng l\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?\f0\lang1033 t bi\f1\lang1066\u7879?\f0\lang1033 n ph\'e1p b\f1\lang1066\u7843?\f0\lang1033 o m\f1\lang1066\u7853?\f0\lang1033 t hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?\f0\lang1033 u qu\f1\lang1066\u7843?\f0\lang1033 .)\par
