\u8239?\u8239? \par
Lorsque\u8239?cette\u8239?information ne\u8239?lui\u8239?a pas\u8239?\'e9t\'e9\u8239?adress\'e9e\u8239?conform\'e9ment\u8239?aux dispositions du premier\u8239?alin\'e9a, le\u8239?consommateur\u8239?peut\u8239?mettre\u8239?gratuitement\u8239?un\u8239?terme\u8239?au\u8239?contrat, \'e0 tout moment \'e0\u8239?compter\u8239?de la date de reconduction.\u8239? \par
\u8239?\u8239? \par
Les\u8239?avances\u8239?effectu\'e9es\u8239?apr\'e8s la\u8239?derni\'e8re\u8239?date de reconduction\u8239?ou,\u8239?s'agissant\u8239?des\u8239?contrats\u8239?\'e0 dur\'e9e\u8239?ind\'e9termin\'e9e, apr\'e8s la date de transformation du\u8239?contrat\u8239?initial \'e0 dur\'e9e\u8239?d\'e9termin\'e9e,\u8239?sont\u8239?dans\u8239?ce\u8239?cas\u8239?rembours\'e9es\u8239?dans un\u8239?d\'e9lai\u8239?de\u8239?trente\u8239?jours\u8239?\'e0\u8239?compter\u8239?de la date de\u8239?r\'e9siliation,\u8239?d\'e9duction\u8239?faite\u8239?des\u8239?sommes\u8239?correspondant,\u8239?jusqu'\'e0\u8239?celle-ci, \'e0\u8239?l'ex\'e9cution\u8239?du\u8239?contrat.\u8239? \par
\u8239?\u8239? \par
Les dispositions du\u8239?pr\'e9sent\u8239?article\u8239?s'appliquent\u8239?sans\u8239?pr\'e9judice\u8239?de\u8239?celles\u8239?qui\u8239?soumettent\u8239?l\'e9galement\u8239?certains\u8239?contrats\u8239?\'e0 des\u8239?r\'e8gles\u8239?particuli\'e8res\u8239?en\u8239?ce\u8239?qui\u8239?concerne\u8239?l'information\u8239?du\u8239?consommateur.\u8239? \par
